### Booking Rescheduled Event

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/developing/guides/automation/webhooks.mdx

This snippet details the payload structure for a booking that has been rescheduled.

```APIDOC
## Booking Rescheduled Event Payload

### Description
This payload represents the data associated with a booking that has been rescheduled to a new time.

### Method
N/A (Webhook/Event Data)

### Endpoint
N/A (Webhook/Event Data)

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **triggerEvent** (string) - The type of event, "BOOKING_RESCHEDULED".
- **createdAt** (string) - The timestamp when the event was created.
- **payload** (object) - Contains details about the booking.
  - **bookerUrl** (string) - The URL of the booker.
  - **title** (string) - The title of the event.
  - **startTime** (string) - The new start time of the booking in ISO 8601 format.
  - **endTime** (string) - The new end time of the booking in ISO 8601 format.
  - **additionalNotes** (string) - Any additional notes for the booking.
  - **type** (string) - The type of the event.
  - **description** (string) - The description of the event.
  - **eventTypeId** (integer) - The ID of the event type.
  - **hideCalendarNotes** (boolean) - Whether to hide notes in the calendar event.
  - **hideCalendarEventDetails** (boolean) - Whether to hide event details in the calendar event.
  - **hideOrganizerEmail** (boolean) - Whether to hide the organizer's email.
  - **schedulingType** (string|null) - The type of scheduling.
  - **seatsPerTimeSlot** (integer|null) - Number of seats available per time slot.
  - **seatsShowAttendees** (boolean) - Whether to show attendees.
  - **seatsShowAvailabilityCount** (boolean) - Whether to show availability count.
  - **customReplyToEmail** (string|null) - Custom reply-to email address.
  - **disableRescheduling** (boolean) - Whether rescheduling is disabled.
  - **disableCancelling** (boolean) - Whether cancelling is disabled.
  - **organizer** (object) - Details about the event organizer.
    - **id** (integer) - The organizer's ID.
    - **name** (string) - The organizer's name.
    - **email** (string) - The organizer's email address.
    - **timeZone** (string) - The organizer's time zone.
    - **language** (object)
      - **locale** (string) - The organizer's language locale.
    - **utcOffset** (integer) - The organizer's UTC offset.

### Request Example
```json
{
  "triggerEvent": "BOOKING_RESCHEDULED",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "payload": {
    "bookerUrl": "https://app.example.com",
    "title": "Strategy Session: Organizer & Guest",
    "startTime": "2024-01-10T14:30:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-10T14:45:00Z",
    "additionalNotes": "Standard meeting notes placeholder",
    "type": "standard-event-type",
    "description": "Standard meeting notes placeholder",
    "eventTypeId": 100,
    "hideCalendarNotes": false,
    "hideCalendarEventDetails": false,
    "hideOrganizerEmail": false,
    "schedulingType": null,
    "seatsPerTimeSlot": null,
    "seatsShowAttendees": true,
    "seatsShowAvailabilityCount": true,
    "customReplyToEmail": null,
    "disableRescheduling": false,
    "disableCancelling": false,
    "organizer": {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Organizer Name",
      "email": "organizer@example.com",
      "timeZone": "UTC",
      "language": {"locale": "en"},
      "utcOffset": 0
    }
  }
}
```

### Response
#### Success Response (200)
N/A (This is event data, not a direct API response)

#### Response Example
N/A
```

